title: Overweight to Pay? Plus Dr. V's Top 7
description:
If you're overweight should you pay more for your healthcare? Then Jillian is joined by Dr. Katja Van Herle, UCLA board certified endocrinologist, to give us her Top 7 ways to fight off flu this winter.
